      "content": "so i was sitting in this cafe today and i kept looking at this specific chipped blue mug on the shelf. i don't know why but i had this really intense feeling that it was \"going\" to be part of something big, like i saw a flash of a news report about a plane crash in my head just by looking at the crack in the mug. then like 2 hours later the news actually broke about a crash. i feel like i'm losing it but it felt so real. have u ever heard of people seeing stuff like that?",
